    "en": {
      "title": "Reserved seat fares for trains increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Department of Railways said that fares for reserved seats for long-distance services and inter-city express trains will be increased from today (1).",
        "This increase applies to first, second, and third class reserved train seats.",
        "These fares are being increased along with the increase in the price of the train tickets on the last 22nd."
      ],
